titleInfo.title: International Brotherhood of Electrical Workers Local No. 43 Pension, Annuity and Health and Welfare Funds et al v. JPL Electric, Inc.
titleInfo.subTitle: MEMORANDUM-DECISION&ORDER: denying the # 9 Motion to Dismiss for Lack of Prosecution; and granting the # 10 Motion for Default Judgment, the Clerk is directed to enter default judgment in favor of the plaintiffs' and against defendant JPL Electric, Inc., for the sum of $122,466.34, plus interest thereon at the rate provided for by 28 USC section 1961(a). Signed by Judge Norman A. Mordue on 1/29/07. (jmb)
